---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
---

<div
  class="flex flex-col container mx-auto px-20 md:px-72 items-center justify-center my-12 md:my-24"
>
  <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-7xl text-center">Beyond just accurate</h2>
  <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-7xl text-center mb-8 md:mb-12">transcriptions</h2>
  <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-center">
    Recordings are enhanced by combining multiple advanced transcription
    features to ensure accuracy and context you can trust, supporting multiple
    speakers in 112 languages.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 md:mt-12 px-20 md:px-64">
  <div class="flex justify-between gap-8 md:gap-20">
    <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <strong class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-red-500">
        Speaker labels
      </strong>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl">112+ languages</p>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl relative">Transcript auto-paragraphing</p>
    </div>
    <Image src="/beyond.png" alt="beyond" width="500" height="500" />
  </div>
</div>
